{"tid":923354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女遭淫師猥褻　父請學校領導吃飯竟暴斃","createTime":"2018-12-01T07:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T11:07:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6fa6cd2d976b4ccba4e160cf3a89018b3e8724","tid":923354,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"中國湖南衡南縣清泉學校，一名15歲高一女生「木子」(化名)，遭到數學老師胡姓男子猥褻亂親，事後校方將胡男解雇。木子的父親感激學校的介入相助，請了學校領導吃飯，但就在飯局中，木子父親劉姓男子竟然暴斃身亡。<br />\n據中國《新浪新聞》報導，木子在本月14日晚間6點多，找了胡姓老師溝通補課，但遭胡男強行摟抱、拉手、貼臉，木子一再抗拒，但胡男對她說：「你是我的寶貝。」更直接越抱越緊，並把嘴巴貼在木子臉上。<br />\n事發隔日，胡男馬上被校方以違規收費補課，和嚴重違反學校「男教師輔導或約見女生時，要有至少3名同學在場」的規定，被學校解聘。木子父親劉姓男子非常感激校方的處理方式，特別在17日邀請學校領導吃飯，但當天中午劉男卻突然身體不適，送醫搶救後不治身亡。據悉木子父親曾在飯局中，和其他兩名學校領導共飲白酒約1斤2兩，之後這兩名領導也被上級指控在工作期間飲酒，縣教育局已立案調查。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181201/640_ef6f6cd510cc9e42297857113b008207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181201%2F640_ef6f6cd510cc9e42297857113b008207.jpg&h=049d5419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181201/1476490/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181201%2F1476490%2F&d=ZNf2MwaxqR1LA9olbv5jbP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=04e6d7e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181201%2F1476490%2F&h=ed89598b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181201/1476490/</a>"},{"pid":"799d9e14c3985c0b2e5f94cca3e769c38ec1389c","tid":923354,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33068839256bfabf9f423a305b367d49c9ae71c","tid":923354,"uid":196099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"成件事由頭到尾都痴撚柒線"},{"pid":"f26ba93e8cc228be9f190b646b8670694ad13a62","tid":923354,"uid":48066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"學校做正確野竟然要請佢地食飯"},{"pid":"58bfc8966ade3945d7e3f52b872ff0c925c6f86f","tid":923354,"uid":135313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f26ba93e8cc228be9f190b646b8670694ad13a62","tid":923354,"uid":48066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"學校做正確野竟然要請佢地食飯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"這就是支那"},{"pid":"463554137ec95ae6d2a66c7c3205309c3926d160","tid":923354,"uid":11067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"男教師輔導或約見女生時，要有至少3名同學在場<br />\n<br />\n即係一拖三合乎校規<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0a44ffc80b29e9248ea2c300a09edee6b84761","tid":923354,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"463554137ec95ae6d2a66c7c3205309c3926d160","tid":923354,"uid":11067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"男教師輔導或約見女生時，要有至少3名同學在場<br />\n<br />\n即係一拖三合乎校規<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"老師+3個男同學搞一個女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594f4ec778465eed30c24cf5bc672d9b1c34f5c7","tid":923354,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"男教師輔導或約見女生時，要有至少3名同學在場<br />\n<br />\n果然所有男人都係潛在既強姦犯"}]}